videos.description: Jarrett Allen gets the offensive rebound and is able to finish the dunk surrounded by Celtics.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Allen finishes impressive dunk in traffic) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Allen finishes impressive dunk in traffic

videos.description: Jeff Teague's floater falls off the rim, but Tristan Thompson comes down the lane and throws one down.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Thompson follows the miss with two-handed jam) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson follows the miss with two-handed jam

videos.description: Kevin Durant is unable to hit the floater but Jeff Green follows it up with the one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Green ends quarter in style with putback jam) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green ends quarter in style with putback jam

videos.description: Grant Williams throws the pretty bounce pass to Jayson Tatum who flushes it home with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum slams home dunk from Williams' dime) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum slams home dunk from Williams' dime

videos.description: Semi Ojeleye is met by Jarrett Allen at the rim for the block, but Ojeleye gets it back and crams home the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ojeleye gets final laugh on Allen's block with a dunk) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ojeleye gets final laugh on Allen's block with a dunk

videos.description: Kyrie Irving goes up top DeAndre Jordan who has his head at the rim while he dunks it.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan soars to the rim for alley-oop dunk) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan soars to the rim for alley-oop dunk

videos.description: The Nets get out in transition and Kyrie Irving splashes a three from way behind the line.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie's range has no limits as he knocks down deep 3-pointer) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie's range has no limits as he knocks down deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Kevin Durant stares down Tristan Thompson and knocks down the three pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant sizes up Thompson, drains 3) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant sizes up Thompson, drains 3

videos.description: Kevin Durant throws the lob up to DeAndre Jordan for the slam, then on the next possession Kyrie Irving puts in the impressive transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD to Jordan alley-oop and Kyrie’s layup extend Brooklyn’s lead) 2020/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD to Jordan alley-oop and Kyrie's layup extend Brooklyn's lead

videos.description: Kyrie Irving breaks down the Nets Christmas day win over the Celtics and how he's happy with the team's first two victories, but knows it's a long season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Kyrie: Our team more than '7-11') 2020/12/25

videos.headline: Kyrie: Our team more than '7-11'

videos.description: Kyrie Irving goes for 37 while Kevin Durant pours in 29 as the Nets continue hot start to season with dominant win over Celtics.
